Summary: witnessed it around the house and took pictures; witnessed few other objects before it disappeared
divs: Sighting DetailsMy eight yr old son and I were playing in the front yard when we noticed an object about a 1000ft above the house.I ran to the shed and got my binos.I saw other objects in the sky.I grabbed my camera and got off two shots before it vanished.
